================================
     Obstacle Detection
================================
Battery-powered system with a slide switch.

The system detects the presence of an obstacle within a specified threshold distance.

Sensor distance values are displayed on the Arduino Serial Monitor.


================================
Detection Threshold
================================
Any object detected at or below the specified threshold distance will be considered as "Detected".

Else "Not Detected".


